1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Your coffee after 2 PM
is stealing tomorrow's energy.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:08,000
You drink it to survive the afternoon. But caffeine has a half-life of 6 hours.
That 3 PM coffee? Half of it is still in your brain at 9 PM.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Move your last coffee to before 1 PM. It
feels wrong for 3 days. Then your afternoons change.

4
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:28,000
VOLT Sleep gives you 1 action per day
to fix this. Free. Link in bio.

